You could use frisee in
this if you wanted to.

00:14:41.280 --> 00:14:43.930
I'm big into bitter
greens right now, frisee,

00:14:43.930 --> 00:14:47.295
and radicchio's, and triveso's,
and all those Italian ones.

00:14:53.270 --> 00:14:54.941
So we're motoring through that.

00:14:54.941 --> 00:14:56.940
We're going to make our
vinaigrette in a second,

