But it does come with a
guard that will protect you,

00:21:51.090 --> 00:21:53.200
but it will take
like three hours

00:21:53.200 --> 00:21:56.920
to make what you want to
make, so I don't use it.

00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:59.870
But also, like when we
come to a certain point

00:21:59.870 --> 00:22:01.840
to keep the integrity
of our fingers--

00:22:01.840 --> 00:22:03.590
and God, when these
things, when they cut,

00:22:03.590 --> 00:22:06.060
they just so cleanly
and beautifully cut,

00:22:06.060 --> 00:22:10.300
and you're bleeding
everywhere, it's great.

00:22:10.300 --> 00:22:13.287
But it results in
this, and at the speed

00:22:13.287 --> 00:22:15.370
that I did that, it would
take a long time for you

00:22:15.370 --> 00:22:21.470
to do with a knife,
so it's very fast.

00:22:21.470 --> 00:22:26.650
So your comfort,
leisure level, I

00:22:26.650 --> 00:22:29.939
do not want you
to cut yourselves.

00:22:29.939 --> 00:22:31.230
That's going to go to the side.

00:22:31.230 --> 00:22:32.979
I'm going to do a
little bit more on that.

00:22:37.490 --> 00:22:39.950
I hear [INAUDIBLE],
are you like,

