and that's going to give
a nice little bit of color

00:24:22.910 --> 00:24:24.900
to our end results.

00:24:24.900 --> 00:24:28.400
And again this is
two salads, but I

00:24:28.400 --> 00:24:30.425
think the modern realm
of how we eat in America

00:24:30.425 --> 00:24:32.780
has totally changed.

