And it's no longer a
meat and potatoes world,

00:24:34.990 --> 00:24:37.690
so if you had this and some
roasted tofu next to it

00:24:37.690 --> 00:24:41.530
and some brown rice and maybe
another little salad element,

00:24:41.530 --> 00:24:42.590
to me that's dinner.

00:24:42.590 --> 00:24:45.980
We all work a lot, we all do
a lot of stuff, we work out,

00:24:45.980 --> 00:24:50.090
we're always running around
and you want to feel good.

00:24:50.090 --> 00:24:52.680
And a 12 ounce steak
or a massive thing

00:24:52.680 --> 00:24:55.700
is just not feel good food,
it's once a month food now.

00:24:55.700 --> 00:24:59.830
It still exists, and I still
want it, not too often.

00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:03.500
Ate at Mourad last
night, it was good.

00:25:03.500 --> 00:25:08.220
That's that new Moroccan, I
just wish it was more Moroccan,

00:25:08.220 --> 00:25:12.330
but I'll write them a
Yelp review, don't worry.

00:25:12.330 --> 00:25:13.915
I have like 25 Yelp accounts.

00:25:13.915 --> 00:25:16.188
[LAUGHTER]

00:25:19.777 --> 00:25:20.860
HUGH ACHESON: Retribution.

