pretty vigorously, in the oven.

00:25:38.960 --> 00:25:40.420
How are you?

00:25:40.420 --> 00:25:42.500
What's going on?

00:25:42.500 --> 00:25:45.004
Nothing?

00:25:45.004 --> 00:25:51.690
[HUMMING]

