them, then people are like,

00:25:58.050 --> 00:26:00.510
yeah, I don't like anchovies,
they're really salty,

00:26:00.510 --> 00:26:02.426
and you're like, well
yeah, that's because you

00:26:02.426 --> 00:26:04.510
didn't rinse them.

00:26:04.510 --> 00:26:08.406
But you can buy bigger salt
packed anchovies from Italy,

00:26:08.406 --> 00:26:11.030
you can buy the ones like these,
which are salt packed and then

00:26:11.030 --> 00:26:16.770
packed in oil, or you can
buy Spanish boquerones, which

00:26:16.770 --> 00:26:19.990
are again curated in
salt, but then marinated

00:26:19.990 --> 00:26:24.650
in vinegar and olive
oil, and are delicious.

00:26:24.650 --> 00:26:25.150
Delicious.

00:26:27.820 --> 00:26:29.870
What am I doing?

