00:28:12.690 --> 00:28:14.380
Meaning if somebody
doesn't like it,

00:28:14.380 --> 00:28:16.338
you can just stand back
like a Japanese master,

00:28:16.338 --> 00:28:19.290
going whatever, you
don't understand my art.

