And then the anchovies
are going to go over.

00:28:38.224 --> 00:28:40.640
I'm going to get a little bit
more of that frond in there.

00:28:40.640 --> 00:28:44.180
I'm going to add just a little
bit of olive oil to this too.

00:28:44.180 --> 00:28:46.345
If you wanted to,
like if this-- there's

00:28:46.345 --> 00:28:48.720
another part of the book that's
got pickled shrimp in it,

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:50.845
and if you wanted to make
a batch of pickled shrimp

00:28:50.845 --> 00:28:53.810
and then tuck them into
this as a beautiful side.

00:28:53.810 --> 00:28:55.334
And this is meant
as a spread, this

00:28:55.334 --> 00:28:57.750
is again-- it's reactionary
cooking to the farmer's market

00:28:57.750 --> 00:28:58.770
and what's there.

