Then I'm just kind
of repeating this

00:31:58.260 --> 00:32:00.590
and then the onions
are going on.

00:32:00.590 --> 00:32:03.100
The onions are so pretty
though, and onions to me

00:32:03.100 --> 00:32:06.780
are awesome flavor because
they're cooked sugar.

00:32:06.780 --> 00:32:09.030
Onions are the way that
everybody's like, how do I get

00:32:09.030 --> 00:32:10.525
at my kids to eat vegetables?

00:32:10.525 --> 00:32:13.070
I'm like, feed them cooked
onions and beets when they're

00:32:13.070 --> 00:32:15.080
two years old, they'll
never know what candy is,

00:32:15.080 --> 00:32:18.794
because it's got so much
sugar in there already.

00:32:18.794 --> 00:32:20.210
So that's getting
tucked in there.

00:32:20.210 --> 00:32:25.590
If you serve this with a
really good loaf of bread,

00:32:25.590 --> 00:32:28.050
you're just expanding the
idea of what dinner is.

