I go on the side of--
I enjoy acid in food,

00:32:54.860 --> 00:32:56.710
I enjoy brightness in food.

00:32:56.710 --> 00:32:58.070
I like that flavor.

00:32:58.070 --> 00:33:02.670
I think it's sort of bouncy to
me, and redolent and exciting.

00:33:02.670 --> 00:33:06.207
I don't like uber rich
flavors, so the vinaigrette

00:33:06.207 --> 00:33:08.540
