AUDIENCE: What do you like
to cook for your kids?

00:34:00.400 --> 00:34:02.600
Or what do they get really
excited about if you're

00:34:02.600 --> 00:34:03.100
cooking?

00:34:09.483 --> 00:34:11.360
HUGH ACHESON: Steak.

